label: post /v1/characters/{character_id}/mail/
description: Create and send a new mail.

label: post /v2/characters/{character_id}/mail/labels/
description: Create a mail label.

label: put /v1/characters/{character_id}/mail/{mail_id}/
description: Update metadata about a mail.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/orders/
description: List market orders placed by a character.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/corporations/{corporation_id}/orders/
description: List market orders placed on behalf of a corporation.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/markets/{region_id}/history/
description: Return a list of historical market statistics for the specified type in a region.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/markets/{region_id}/orders/
description: Return a list of orders in a region.This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: get /v1/markets/{region_id}/types/
description: Return a list of type IDs that have active orders in the region, for efficient market indexing.This route is cached for up to 600 seconds.

label: get /v1/markets/groups/
description: Get a list of item groups.This route expires daily at 11:05.

label: get /v1/markets/groups/{market_group_id}/
description: Get information on an item group.This route expires daily at 11:05.

label: get /v1/markets/prices/
description: Return a list of prices.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/markets/structures/{structure_id}/
description: Return all orders in a structure.This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/opportunities/
description: Return a list of tasks finished by a character.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/opportunities/groups/
description: Return a list of opportunities groups.This route expires daily at 11:05.

label: get /v1/opportunities/groups/{group_id}/
description: Return information of an opportunities group.This route expires daily at 11:05.

label: get /v1/opportunities/tasks/
description: Return a list of opportunities tasks.This route expires daily at 11:05.

label: get /v1/opportunities/tasks/{task_id}/
description: Return information of an opportunities task.This route expires daily at 11:05.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/planets/
description: Returns a list of all planetary colonies owned by a character.This route is cached for up to 600 seconds.

label: get /v3/characters/{character_id}/planets/{planet_id}/
description: Returns full details on the layout of a single planetary colony, including links, pins and routes. Note: Planetary information is only recalculated when the colony is viewed through the client. Information will not update until this criteria is met.This route is cached for up to 600 seconds.

label: get /v1/corporations/{corporation_id}/customs_offices/
description: List customs offices owned by a corporation.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/universe/schematics/{schematic_id}/
description: Get information on a planetary factory schematic.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/route/{origin}/{destination}/
description: Get the systems between origin and destination.This route is cached for up to 86400 seconds.

label: get /v2/characters/{character_id}/search/
description: Search for entities that match a given sub-string.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/search/
description: Search for entities that match a given sub-string.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/attributes/
description: Return attributes of a character.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.
